📌 Numbered Steps (bottom text translation)

🔹 Japanese:

① 不備入力・決定が揃ったことをもって翌営業日に通知対象となる
② 通知対象申込を抽出
③ 募集人宛にプッシュ通知を発信
④ ネオnetの「新契約進捗状況照会」の進捗状況に反映
（ただし、査定決定不能などの理由で一部は反映されない場合もあり得る）
⑤ プッシュ通知を受け取り、ネオnetの「新契約進捗状況照会」を参照

⸻

🔸 English:

① When both incomplete entry and decision are completed, the case becomes eligible for notification the next business day.
② Extract applications that qualify for notification.
③ Send push notifications to the respective agents.
④ Update the progress status in ネオnet’s “New Contract Progress Inquiry” screen.
　(Some cases, such as “unable to evaluate,” may not be reflected immediately.)
⑤ Recipients check the push notification and refer to the relevant screen in ネオnet.

